title: Canes of Divergence
description: The Newest Addition to The Dusk Gate Chronicles Has Finally Arrived!Things were finally going well for Quinn and William -- a kingdom in check, their enemy behind bars, and a special new someone to celebrate.Until a mysterious danger threatened to take it all.With the gate closed and no way to reach the resources they desperately need, time is running out.Will help from an unexpected source reach them in time?Featuring the return of everyone's favorite characters -- including some old friends we never expected to see again -- Canes of Divergence takes The Dusk Gate Chronicles in a whole new direction.
author: Breeana Puttroff
